2017.assessment:
FH CL=4. Major election year with controversial results; Supreme Court annulment;
re-run boycott. Deaths in post-election protests (37 killed by security forces).
Temporary media blackout ordered by government during protests. Partly Free.

2020.assessment:
Kenyatta-Ruto conflict intensified. BBI constitutional process pushed by Kenyatta-Odinga;
Ruto opposed it. DCI and anti-corruption agencies pursuing Ruto allies. Unusual situation
of sitting president openly undermining his deputy.
